Description: Flexible and user-friendly probabilistic segmentation of time series with 
    smooth and/or abrupt regime changes by a mixture model-based regression approach with 
    a hidden logistic process, fitted by the EM algorithm. See also the packages 'PWR', 
    'HMMR' and 'MRHLP'.
